headline: Breathable Membranes Research Report 2025
summary: The global breathable membranes market, valued at $1.74 billion in 2023, is projected to reach $3.27 billion by 2029, growing at a CAGR of approximately 11% from 2024 to 2029. Rising demand for sustainable building materials, enhanced material technology, and increasing awareness of indoor air quality drive this growth. headline: DuPont Launches Medical Grade Liquid Silicone Rubber Series
summary: DD launches Liveo C6-8XX medical-grade liquid silicone rubber, offering lower viscosity, faster molding and USP Class VI compliance for advanced devices.
